{"tid":209064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"壞手機失功課大專生跳樓亡","createTime":"2017-04-20T02:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T05:19:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59eb4f6b942dbd0caeae80b03ec79a1b69609a02","tid":209064,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:17:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19995630&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19995630%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170420&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=8a847754\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19995630%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170420&h=7aeb61b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19995630&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170420</a><br />\n<br />\n壞手機失功課大專生跳樓亡<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n死者家人到現場認屍。 鄭文輝攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名就讀香港大學專業進修學院（HKU SPACE）男生，昨凌晨在香港仔寓所墮樓，救護員到場證實已死亡。警方撿獲遺書，相信事主因手機損壞導致儲存的功課等重要資料流失，擔心影響學業而輕生，案件無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n擔心影響學業<br />\n<br />\n20歲死者姓陳，為HKU SPACE學生，同學都稱呼他阿鋒。阿鋒生前與父母及兩姊同住在漁安苑瑚安閣一單位，過往在區內中學畢業，曾是羽毛球校隊，亦擔任學生會幹事。去年，他相約朋友一同旅行，並把相片上載社交網站，陳父亦給予「like」。詎料明原本朝氣勃勃的阿鋒突然墮樓，家人都傷心不已。<br />\n昨凌晨2時許，阿鋒從住所墮樓，倒地昏迷。途人聽聞巨響報警，救護員到場證實他已死亡。《蘋果》於意外後向HKU SPACE查詢，但至截稿前未獲回覆。<br />\n■記者張培生"},{"pid":"d4d03c943ac30615f05628172d6260a6a4da069e","tid":209064,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:18:14.000Z","msg":"無 backup ?"},{"pid":"e1b989fccc83ef217df6694b5bca0bedbd8f02ee","tid":209064,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:19:14.000Z","msg":"似另有內情喎"},{"pid":"8d76c28199b1db5e40acd50089134afb65243b4b","tid":209064,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:20:27.000Z","msg":"舊聞黎啦"},{"pid":"8e072bc33b5e86a1da384a52e4a311736bf6d9fa","tid":209064,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:20:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6474764c9c2060ef37bd4a09971c53aebb3d0707","tid":209064,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:21:15.000Z","msg":"old news is so_______"},{"pid":"4962fbf65079ef333696bf02e8e35aa5a93f6438","tid":209064,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:21:22.000Z","msg":"垃圾太空人不意外"},{"pid":"2f4474cabebc551a028b07bd8439df9e22112542","tid":209064,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:22:15.000Z","msg":"飛行模式失靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbce302a0c4e11a60fe34ddfdce024c54e64cef","tid":209064,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾太空人不意外</blockquote><br />\n咩太空人 ?"},{"pid":"ea6eeb1d37e774258b64bd39855b30eb71f621a8","tid":209064,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飛行模式失靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n??"},{"pid":"31ad13c7dada93301c36d12e9c311faa6a600d1b","tid":209064,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似另有內情喎</blockquote><br />\n我都唔係好信"},{"pid":"9fbcb3bf230f0fa104a095fb0767c42b3aa61839","tid":209064,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:26:45.000Z","msg":"唔見左唔交咪得囉<br />\n最多咪retake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d0f2e62e8c575e97ee6d0b9705944fe8f80b8d","tid":209064,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:27:33.000Z","msg"